Often little people cannot be seen between parked cars.  Pedestrians need the ability walk safely across Van Buren to enjoy our park.

Your consideration of this request is greatly appreciated.  Please let us know if there is any more that we can do to get these requests fulfilled.   Thank you.

Sincerely,
 
 
Gina Douglas
Friends of Takoma Recreation Center
